snippet.title: Berzerk Ball 2 - Official Trailer !
snippet.description:
Trailer of our newest and upcoming game, Berzerk Ball 2 !!!
The sequel of a game played over 40 million times already, and counting !
Level-up, upgrade, equip weapons and boosters, forge unique weapons, challenge your friend and blast the geek out of the orbit !  Coming soon !
